name: FoodPicker
0:
”Alexa, open food picker.”
”Alexa, ask food picker what is best between pasta and pizza”
”Alexa, ask food picker should we have croissant or pancakes?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food picker
des:
The skill for when you cannot make up your mind on what to eat.
Offered two types of food, it chooses one at random and returns it.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
